apply_monitor_palette                 leay      >pals2,pcr                                ; advance/derive Y so it addresses a field in the PCR-indexed structure for the next game control flow item.
                                      lda       >projection_row_workspace+$12E            ; fetch workspace location >projection_row_workspace+$12E for the current game control flow decision/calculation.
